item.title: New hosting and code optimization
item.dc:creator: singlepagefolio-usr
item.content:encoded:
As a Christmas present I decided to change hosting and improve the navigation speed optimizing the site's code. This in order to achieve a better and faster user experience. After several tests the previous hosting resulted being quite slow, so I decided to invest more and change it. For a more complete work I optimized the web portfolio using the w3 total cache plug in, especially customizing the files minification. Enjoy the new faster navigation!
